"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"***Related: [Reserve Bank warns Aussies over punting on ‘fad driven’ cryptocurrencies](https://cointelegraph.com/news/rba-warns-aussies-over-punting-on-fad-driven-cryptocurrencies)***\\n\\nThe RBA said that it has [explored the concept](https://cointelegraph.com/news/reserve-bank-of-australia-still-researching-the-cbdc-it-says-it-doesn-t-need) of CBDCs since 2018 —despite [playing down its importance](https://cointelegraph.com/news/no-need-for-central-bank-digital-currency-in-australia-says-reserve-bank) on multiple occasions — but has gradually ramped up its focus on a digital currency since 2020 amid [growing interest](https://cointelegraph.com/news/japanese-megabanks-join-consortium-launching-yen-based-digital-currency) from governments across the globe, citing China in particular who has already rolled out numerous [public trials of the digital yuan](https://cointelegraph.com/news/chinese-retail-giant-jd-accepts-digital-yuan-payments-for-singles-day)\",\"timestamp\":1639042513,\"title\":\"indicated that the monetary authorities prefer to use targeted\"},\"digest\":\"VjWXUnzr18DKzBhcUkydICpi4Hcfx-R5oTz2WD6wpFY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xc30C6e8ea603a4127a1c6429a7196136374E8964\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"OsNCrD0pmOaFRpjFT3OwWdp44yDCZP8-k_i58245kII\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"bzGLyuNj0_x8fO7xd1Q_HIGuBMYOsVhTUaPdAQ5YzY0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"eNy7aJ9ZtPmdVpc-dLvSfpS0pbPd0M39RgcXWj6v3wHSRzVZTMllhVpCkrQYL5nbRszWTGkrKbPP5VUcMXJCRg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x7115f9f2f1991f39e9be1bd2c4f480b7c7ee3404b2e8936b3155ba0d82f80a765f4373a9cb31403bf547d06608f7494c260edca04caba33995e2e3f41b760f211b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"OsNCrD0pmOaFRpjFT3OwWdp44yDCZP8-k_i58245kII\\\",\\\